"If the new regulation is implemented safely - and we work closely with the airline in this respect - both sides will benefit from it," said Glading.
We are honestly sorry to have to feel like guards on this issue.
However, Internet connections to surfing, exchanging e-mails, text messages or downloading data below three kilometres remained prohibited, the Authority explained.
